\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {1}{\ignorespaces  (a) The overall architecture of MSL-UNet. (b) VSS Block is the main construction of our encoder. (c) Strip Large-kernel grouped attention gate(SLGAG) can enhance features from skip connections. (d) Multi-scale Strip Large-kernel convolutional block(MSLCB), progressing patches in all dimensions to further enhance features, is main construction of our decoder. (e) Strip convolutional block(SC). (f) Channel attention block(CA). (g) Spatial attention block(SA). (h) Multi-scale attention block(MA). (i) Strip block. (j) Strip module. (k) Feed-Forward Network(FFN). }}{4}{figure.caption.2}\protected@file@percent }
\providecommand*\caption@xref[2]{\@setref\relax\@undefined{#1}}
\newlabel{MSL-UNet}{{1}{4}{(a) The overall architecture of MSL-UNet. (b) VSS Block is the main construction of our encoder. (c) Strip Large-kernel grouped attention gate(SLGAG) can enhance features from skip connections. (d) Multi-scale Strip Large-kernel convolutional block(MSLCB), progressing patches in all dimensions to further enhance features, is main construction of our decoder. (e) Strip convolutional block(SC). (f) Channel attention block(CA). (g) Spatial attention block(SA). (h) Multi-scale attention block(MA). (i) Strip block. (j) Strip module. (k) Feed-Forward Network(FFN)}{figure.caption.2}{}}
